Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:24:34.42,WM,,0,0,0,,masssterchief
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:18.05,Text,,0,0,0,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:49.00,Text,,0,0,0,,[Summer Break]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:06.05,Text,,0,0,0,,Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:08.72,Text,,0,0,0,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:12.22,Text,,0,0,0,,She said that she won't do anything today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:18.52,Text,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:21.42,Text,,0,0,0,,She wants ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.52,0:02:25.75,Text,,0,0,0,,Get it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:28.70,Text,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:35.17,Text,,0,0,0,,She wants the grape flavor one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.91,Text,,0,0,0,,How can you tell, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:46.32,Text,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:57.80,Text,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, it's about time that you go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:02:59.17,Text,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:03.37,Text,,0,0,0,,Do you want to come with me, Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:09.65,Text,,0,0,0,,Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:17.70,Text,,0,0,0,,I already declared that I won't do anything today...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:20.50,Text,,0,0,0,,No one has approved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:27.70,Text,,0,0,0,,How are things at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:30.75,Text,,0,0,0,,We all build plastic models the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:33.80,Text,,0,0,0,,5 Doms.\N-What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:35.87,Text,,0,0,0,,What kind of workplace is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:39.67,Text,,0,0,0,,It's about time that you get a girlfriend, Big Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.40,Text,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:59.07,Text,,0,0,0,,Can't you come home more often?\N-I'm really busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:02.87,Text,,0,0,0,,You have that look on your face.\N-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:05.10,Text,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:10.50,Text,,0,0,0,,You obviously lack vitamin D.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:11.72,Text,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:19.12,Text,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:22.32,Text,,0,0,0,,Where is Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:25.37,Text,,0,0,0,,He's spending 3 days and 2 nights hiking with the hiking club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:28.42,Text,,0,0,0,,Even though his daughter came home, such a free spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:30.85,Text,,0,0,0,,That's your father all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.07,Text,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.42,Text,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:38.17,Text,,0,0,0,,I heard from Auntie that you're back, so here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:39.30,Text,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:40.70,Text,,0,0,0,,Here are some grapes from our farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.60,Text,,0,0,0,,You're the best, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.37,Text,,0,0,0,,Best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:49.35,Text,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.92,Text,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for joining in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:52.32,Text,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.\N-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:58.02,Text,,0,0,0,,This meat is so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:01.80,Text,,0,0,0,,It's done, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.67,Text,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:08.42,Text,,0,0,0,,I chose good meat.\N-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:11.00,Text,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:12.87,Text,,0,0,0,,You don't eat enough vegetables, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.32,Text,,0,0,0,,I was eyeing that meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:16.15,Text,,0,0,0,,You gained weight in Tokyo, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:19.00,Text,,0,0,0,,What? What do you think, Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:20.65,Text,,0,0,0,,Has your face gotten rounder?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:22.05,Text,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:25.02,Text,,0,0,0,,I'm against bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:26.37,Text,,0,0,0,,Eat some vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:28.45,Text,,0,0,0,,Vegetables please.\N-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.05,Text,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:33.97,Text,,0,0,0,,Look, I caught it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.17,Text,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:36.99,Text,,0,0,0,,That's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.90,Text,,0,0,0,,We used to keep one as a pet, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:41.30,Text,,0,0,0,,Kabuto Juuzou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:43.15,Text,,0,0,0,,You cried really hard when it died, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:45.65,Text,,0,0,0,,You should have lied and said that it ran away.\N-No no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:49.40,Text,,0,0,0,,He can't lie when he was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.90,Text,,0,0,0,,Right?\N-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.55,Text,,0,0,0,,That's the only good thing about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:54.24,Text,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:55.50,Text,,0,0,0,,No no no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:06:00.72,Text,,0,0,0,,Who wants to eat yakisoba?\N-Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:02.85,Text,,0,0,0,,Let's make it.\N-Should I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:06.80,Text,,0,0,0,,Big Bro's yakisoba is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:09.35,Text,,0,0,0,,Someone who makes bad yakisoba is actually impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:12.32,Text,,0,0,0,,Looking good.\N-Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.82,Text,,0,0,0,,Do you want to add some meat?\N-Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.47,Text,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:18.20,Text,,0,0,0,,That's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.55,Text,,0,0,0,,It's everyone's meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:20.92,Text,,0,0,0,,Let's mix it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:22.60,Text,,0,0,0,,It's okay, right?\N-Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:24.42,Text,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:26.07,Text,,0,0,0,,It's everyone's meat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:32.85,Text,,0,0,0,,That looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:34.32,Text,,0,0,0,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:12.27,Text,,0,0,0,,Plastic model?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:14.35,Text,,0,0,0,,That's a blast from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:16.02,Text,,0,0,0,,What is this called again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:18.02,Text,,0,0,0,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:19.90,Text,,0,0,0,,It's Dad's Mazinger Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.07,Text,,0,0,0,,Your brother got it, but
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:25.37,Text,,0,0,0,,you said that you also want one, so you wrote your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:32.55,Text,,0,0,0,,Back then, you loved your brother so much that you'd imitate everything that he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.50,Text,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:45.97,Text,,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:47.97,Text,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, this Mazinger...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:48.97,Text,,0,0,0,,Let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:51.20,Text,,0,0,0,,Let's get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.15,Text,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:05.05,Text,,0,0,0,,What? A marriage proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:07.90,Text,,0,0,0,,The two of you are dating each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:17.62,Text,,0,0,0,,That's What They Call Love in This World!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:26.73,Upper,,0,0,0,,[Sambomaster - Sekai wa Sore wo Ai to Yobundaze]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:26.73,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What connects each new day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:29.80,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is the new you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:34.04,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We make sure of it for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:37.71,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what they call love in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:40.25,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't realize that connecting the voices
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.21,Text,,0,0,0,,What is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:43.90,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of the heart could be so terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:45.35,Text,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan is crying her heart out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:47.12,Text,,0,0,0,,He finally said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.12,Text,,0,0,0,,You knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:52.97,Text,,0,0,0,,He's no longer belongs to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:57.75,Text,,0,0,0,,He's not my son nor your big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:02.22,Text,,0,0,0,,He's going to become Yuki-chan's husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:06.15,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}LOVE & PEACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.57,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}LOVE & PEACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:11.02,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}LOVE & PEACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:13.82,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}LOVE & PEACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.65,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}LOVE & PEACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:21.65,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}LOVE & PEACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:29.70,Text,,0,0,0,,Riko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:30.77,Text,,0,0,0,,Riko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:32.30,Text,,0,0,0,,Riko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:33.52,Text,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.10,Text,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:37.82,Text,,0,0,0,,It was a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:40.05,Text,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.25,Text,,0,0,0,,That's a Mazinger Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:47.22,Text,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:56.18,Text,,0,0,0,,My memory after the marriage proposal is hazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:58.87,Text,,0,0,0,,So you congratulated your big brother on getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:02.22,Text,,0,0,0,,I couldn't congratulate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:06.26,Text,,0,0,0,,As a person, you should say congratulations to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:13.57,Text,,0,0,0,,I want to not think about anything right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:22.65,Text,,0,0,0,,Riko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:26.35,Text,,0,0,0,,Let's not think about anything with this today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:29.32,Text,,0,0,0,,Mazinger Z! You do have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:32.42,Text,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:36.20,Text,,0,0,0,,It's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.82,Text,,0,0,0,,It's the same 1/144 scale, but
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:42.75,Text,,0,0,0,,INFINITY has a complete different setting and size of the robot than the anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:45.97,Text,,0,0,0,,INFINITY? It's not an anime?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:52.22,Text,,0,0,0,,Mazinger Z is the original super robot anime that first aired in 1972.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:56.24,Text,,0,0,0,,In 2018, Mazinger Z / INFINITY The Movie depicts the world
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:59.37,Text,,0,0,0,,10 years after the last episode of the anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:02.70,Text,,0,0,0,,So that's why it looks different than this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:07.00,Text,,0,0,0,,Alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:11.56,Text,,0,0,0,,Open the box!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:16.57,Text,,0,0,0,,The colors already looks strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.32,Text,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:52.85,Text,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:08.72,Text,,0,0,0,,Muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.72,Text,,0,0,0,,The fine details.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:14.40,Text,,0,0,0,,It's not just a moving hunk of steel,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:17.06,Text,,0,0,0,,you can see the gaps in between when the robot moves,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:19.10,Text,,0,0,0,,that gap is it's uniqueness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:22.17,Text,,0,0,0,,There are gaps in between the panels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:23.77,Text,,0,0,0,,It's like a turtle's shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:25.40,Text,,0,0,0,,You did well to notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:30.40,Text,,0,0,0,,The design is denser and more authentic than past works.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.50,Text,,0,0,0,,The workmanship is massive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:34.82,Text,,0,0,0,,Massive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:44.28,Text,,0,0,0,,Big Bro and Yuki-chan are getting married...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:53.15,Text,,0,0,0,,Are you against their marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:57.53,Text,,0,0,0,,I'm not against it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:08.72,Text,,0,0,0,,Riko, the parts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.55,Text,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that they could have told me beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:16.57,Text,,0,0,0,,I see that you're the only one who didn't know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:21.07,Text,,0,0,0,,Is that why he only gave the meat to Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:24.10,Text,,0,0,0,,You didn't get any meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:25.67,Text,,0,0,0,,He only gave me vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.10,Text,,0,0,0,,You need to eat more vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:40.30,Text,,0,0,0,,He never hide anything from me when we were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:43.80,Text,,0,0,0,,It must be sad to be left in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:47.20,Text,,0,0,0,,Do you normally propose in your parents house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.47,Text,,0,0,0,,That's the first time that I heard such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:52.92,Text,,0,0,0,,To think that he sang after his marriage proposal was accepted...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.95,Text,,0,0,0,,Why Sambomaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:57.15,Text,,0,0,0,,That's also the first time that I heard such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:00.25,Text,,0,0,0,,That was horror. A summer ghost story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:04.12,Text,,0,0,0,,You looked like a zombie in the front of the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:06.12,Text,,0,0,0,,Even my mom cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:08.70,Text,,0,0,0,,I wanted to cry with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.92,Text,,0,0,0,,Had I known, we could have be happy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:17.31,Text,,0,0,0,,Is that is what you're currently feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:39.40,Text,,0,0,0,,If only I could say congratulation back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:02.90,Text,,0,0,0,,What pose should I choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:05.42,Text,,0,0,0,,Yassan woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:07.87,Text,,0,0,0,,Riko, choose the pose carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:12.07,Text,,0,0,0,,You can recreate 5 special moves with INFINITY.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:14.87,Text,,0,0,0,,If you use the display that comes with the set,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:17.15,Text,,0,0,0,,you can display it a powerful flying pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:20.55,Text,,0,0,0,,Iron Cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:23.80,Text,,0,0,0,,Good choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:26.10,Text,,0,0,0,,Pilder on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.35,0:15:34.90,Text,,0,0,0,,Give bi...\N-Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.90,Text,,0,0,0,,Big Bro getting married means that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:49.97,Text,,0,0,0,,I will be getting a new family member, a big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:52.62,Text,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought looking at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:16:00.32,Text,,0,0,0,,This wing represents a memory with my big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.57,Text,,0,0,0,,You can switch them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:12.17,Text,,0,0,0,,You know how to use glue, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:16.70,Text,,0,0,0,,Yes. Kumamoto Castle has prepared me for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:36.25,Text,,0,0,0,,You've done a good job mixing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.67,Text,,0,0,0,,Mixing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:42.57,Text,,0,0,0,,It's a method of combining parts from multiple kits to create a combined kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:46.30,Text,,0,0,0,,Across time, combining old and new.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.95,Text,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle that is possible because it's the same plastic model.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.92,Text,,0,0,0,,A miracle that combines the old and new...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:13.02,Text,,0,0,0,,Across time, combining old and new.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:16.75,Text,,0,0,0,,Is she sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:28.92,Text,,0,0,0,,Mazinger Z, give birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:34.62,Text,,0,0,0,,My Big Bro is going to pick me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:43.90,Text,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for today.\N-Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.37,Text,,0,0,0,,Riko, Mazin Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:48.90,Text,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:00.00,Text,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:15.95,Text,,0,0,0,,That's a plastic model shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:17.10,Text,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:19.72,Text,,0,0,0,,My oasis in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:26.75,Text,,0,0,0,,Big Bro.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:39.47,Text,,0,0,0,,The wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:42.15,Text,,0,0,0,,It's now really big.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:45.25,Text,,0,0,0,,Yes. I switched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:46.75,Text,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:48.72,Text,,0,0,0,,This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.32,Text,,0,0,0,,So cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:08.37,Text,,0,0,0,,The traffic light is green.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:24.25,Text,,0,0,0,,I was going to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:27.35,Text,,0,0,0,,that we're dating when you returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:29.02,Text,,0,0,0,,I talked to Yuki about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:32.25,Text,,0,0,0,,Why did you propose to her then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:34.25,Text,,0,0,0,,Just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:38.00,Text,,0,0,0,,I wasn't planning to propose in my parents house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.42,Text,,0,0,0,,But you screamed your lungs out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:45.20,Text,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since you returned home,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:47.82,Text,,0,0,0,,and Yuki was also there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:52.95,Text,,0,0,0,,Mom looked like she's having a lot of fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:59.65,Text,,0,0,0,,I started thinking that family is a great thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.87,Text,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:03.15,Text,,0,0,0,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:15.22,Text,,0,0,0,,Big Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:17.02,Text,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:24.10,Text,,0,0,0,,Thank you for getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:26.32,Text,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:30.17,Text,,0,0,0,,You should have said congratulations.\N-Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:32.45,Text,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:35.20,Text,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:37.17,Text,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.37,Text,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.23,0:20:49.22,Text,,0,0,0,,14, 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:51.07,Text,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:53.05,Text,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:54.55,Text,,0,0,0,,Move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:56.42,Text,,0,0,0,,Go go go go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:58.60,Text,,0,0,0,,Iron Cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:04.37,Text,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:07.12,Text,,0,0,0,,You're going to have more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:09.65,Text,,0,0,0,,It's delicious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.52,0:21:12.55,Text,,0,0,0,,When are you going to come back next?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:15.12,Text,,0,0,0,,Our service is about to start,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:16.90,Text,,0,0,0,,so probably not any time soon.\N-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:21.32,Text,,0,0,0,,You're the president after all, right?\N-I'm the CEO.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:24.54,Text,,0,0,0,,Please excuse my rudeness.\N-It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:37.62,Text,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:38.90,Text,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:41.32,Text,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on the wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:42.92,Text,,0,0,0,,What's with you all of the sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:44.65,Text,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:47.35,Text,,0,0,0,,Wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:48.69,Text,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:49.62,Text,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:52.35,Text,,0,0,0,,It's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:55.95,Text,,0,0,0,,Don't fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:21:57.22,Text,,0,0,0,,It's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.74,0:22:03.57,Text,,0,0,0,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:04.60,Text,,0,0,0,,This is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:09.22,Text,,0,0,0,,This is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:10.57,Text,,0,0,0,,So pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:12.90,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what they call
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:12.90,Upper,,0,0,0,,[Sambomaster - Sekai wa Sore wo Ai to Yobundaze]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.27,0:22:15.25,Text,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:18.42,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}love in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.42,0:22:19.75,Text,,0,0,0,,You're so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:24.67,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the new you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:30.80,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We make sure of it for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.80,0:22:31.92,Text,,0,0,0,,This looks like Big Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:36.80,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:41.00,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as if the past
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.55,0:22:43.22,Text,,0,0,0,,{\i1}never existed.
